"breadcrumbs" : "Sysdig Documentation \/ Sysdig Monitor \/ Alerts \/ Configure Alerts \/ Open the Alert Wizard", 
"snippet" : "There are multiple ways to access the Alert wizard: From the Explore Table Select the Alert (bell) icon beside an entity: Click the More Options (three dots) icon for the table, and select Create a New Alert: From Dashboards Panel Click the More Options (three dots) icon for a panel, and select Crea...", 
