"snippet" : "Use standard ASCII characters, we suggest also to use . namespaces as we do for all our metrics. Allowed characters: a-z A-Z 0-9 _ . For more information on adding parameters to a container agent's configuration file, see the FAQ: How Can I Edit the Agents Configuration File . Installation and Confi...", 
