"snippet" : "The request should set the HTTP header: Accept: application\/json Every response is returned with the HTTP header Content-Type: application\/json;charset=UTF-8 To reduce the size of the request and (primarily) the response, you can set the header to compress HTTP body and response: Accept-Encoding:gzi...", 
