"snippet" : "Containerd resource limits not reported Previous releases of the Sysdig Agent did not report several metrics for containerd-based systems. This issue has been resolved. libnss_db package crash in Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7 A behavior change with the Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7 libnss_db package cause...", 
