"snippet" : "eBPF Probe Build Issues Fixed eBPF probe builds for the 5.0 kernel. Kubernetes API Server Stalls Until Agent Restart An issue occurred where the agent’s communication with the Kubernetes API server could stall until a restart of the agent. This was caused by a flag that was added in the 0.89.1 relea...", 
