"snippet" : "CVEs Resolved The Jackson JSON processor package was updated to address the following list of CVEs: CVE-2018-14718, CVE-2018-12022, CVE-2018-12023, CVE-2018-11307, CVE-2018-14719, CVE-2018-14720, CVE-2018-14721, CVE-2018-19362, CVE-2018-19360, and CVE-2018-19361 App Checks Fixed errors in the Redis ...", 
