"snippet" : "Solr AppCheck refactor: added default 5 second timeout to HTTP requests, get index size from core stats if replication handler is not available, performance improvements. Adding processes with AppCheck metrics to top process list to send to the collector. To prevent sdjagent restarts, we now send he...", 
